window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Book 2 of River of Fate!</p> <p>Darkness rises in Dragonwell, but the Sunset Knight will face it.</p> <p>Legends of the Imperial Knights are older than the Starfall Empire itself. Their titles have been passed down for thousands of years, from the mists of a forgotten era, one that gave rise to powers greater than anything seen today.</p> <p>While searching for the source, Verse discovers the ruins of the Italith and an even older civilization.</p> <p>One that reveals his true heritage.</p> <p>*This is a xianxia immortal cultivation story. It focuses on reincarnation, jade and sunset magic, and primordial bloodlines.</p>"; 
